阻塞式输入流  input() 函数
【注意 】 ：
          input() 函数输入的内容都是字符串类型

name = input('please input your name :')
print('the name is : %s' % name)

运行结果  ：
please input your name :wanghognchang
the name is : wanghognchang


【简单练习一下input输入操作】
print('''
    **********************************
        Welcome  To  Fish 
    **********************************
''')

name = input('Please input your name : ')
password = input('Please input your password : ')
print('Dear %s ,your coins is not enought,please invest more money first ! ' % name)
money = input('invest more money first : ')

print('%s has invested %d success!' % (name, int(money)))

运行结果 ：
**********************************
        Welcome  To  Fish 
**********************************

Please input your name : qwe
Please input your password : qwe
Dear qwe ,your coins is not enought,please invest more money first : 
invest more money first : 123
qwe has invested 123 success!
